rows.label: qst002503_msg0002
rows.name: Huh? Where's Mylak? He's not here, mo?

rows.label: qst002503_msg0003
rows.name:
Mylak... Did he want me to
get eaten by monsters, mo?

rows.label: qst002503_msg0004
rows.name:
We've been adventuring together
for so long... I'm shocked, mo!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0006
rows.name: Tell him Mylak is waiting anxiously.

rows.label: qst002503_msg0007
rows.name:
Tell him Mylak might
not be worried at all.

rows.label: qst002503_msg0008
rows.name: I see, so he was worried, mo...

rows.label: qst002503_msg0009
rows.name:
Partners make up right away,
even after a fight, mo!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0010
rows.name:
I'll go back to Mylak right away
and put his mind at ease, mo!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0012
rows.name:
That guy is unbelievably
cold-hearted, mo!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm going back to Mylak
and I'm going to lecture
him until he's dead, mo!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0014
rows.name: You all have to come with me, mo!
